OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers continuing this evening. The
OL,7,FCentral Belt should become dry
OL,8,Fovernight, but with some low cloud.
OL,9,FPerhaps the odd thundery shower over
OL,10,FDumfries and Southern Borders.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FAny low cloud burning off to
OL,13,Fleave a dry bright day with some sunny
OL,14,Fspells. Very warm to hot.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FWednesday will be sunny and very warm.
OL,18,FSunny, hot inland Thursday, coastal
OL,19,Fhaar, perhaps some thundery showers
OL,20,Flater. Showery on Friday.
